<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今天的突破性故事|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com是您最新的中国新闻报道和时事的在线来源</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 01:09:37 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>在审查中审查时的空气安全报告未解决</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/air-safety-reporting-under-scrutiny-crashes-lie-unresolved-2025-02-27/</link><description>下个月，自中国东部喷气机撞到山坡上杀死132人以来，有三年的历史，亲戚仍在等待造成中国在三十年来最致命的空中灾难的原因。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 23:52:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/air-safety-reporting-under-scrutiny-crashes-lie-unresolved-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>大使说，中国不会为澳大利亚东部的军事演习道歉。</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-will-not-apologise-military-drills-off-australias-east-ambassador-says-2025-02-27/</link><description>中国驻澳大利亚大使说，周五，他的国家没有理由为在澳大利亚和新西兰之间的国际水域进行的军事演习道歉，这些军事演习迫使至少49次飞行以改变路径。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 23:47:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-will-not-apologise-military-drills-off-australias-east-ambassador-says-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国科技创业公司竞赛，利用XI会议的DeepSeek Fever</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/china-tech-startups-race-capitalise-deepseek-fever-xis-meeting-2025-02-27/</link><description>中国技术初创公司正在竞争新鲜的筹款活动，以利用深发现的对人工智能的热情，以及习近平总统最近对该国私人企业的支持。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 23:03:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/china-tech-startups-race-capitalise-deepseek-fever-xis-meeting-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>早上出价：关税，技术疲劳REV UP月末湍流</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphics-2025-02-27/</link><description>看看亚洲市场的前一天。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 21:49:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphics-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普说，他可能会在chagos群岛上接受英国的交易</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/trump-says-he-is-likely-accept-uk-deal-chagos-islands-2025-02-27/</link><description>唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统周四表示，他倾向于支持英国与夏戈斯群岛（Chagos Islands）的美国英国军事基地的未来，以促进英国首相凯尔·斯塔默（Keir Starmer）的未来。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 19:51:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/trump-says-he-is-likely-accept-uk-deal-chagos-islands-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>官员说</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/mexico-analyzing-more-measures-crack-down-low-cost-shipments-official-says-2025-02-27/</link><description>一位官员周四表示，墨西哥正在权衡进一步的贸易措施，以打击低成本的货物，这是一位大部分来自中国的所谓“ de Minimis”购买后的关税。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 19:32:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/mexico-analyzing-more-measures-crack-down-low-cost-shipments-official-says-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国制造商Hikvision未能推翻我们对设备批准的禁令</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/us-court-rejects-hikvision-bid-lift-fcc-ban-equipment-approvals-2025-02-27/</link><description>美国上诉法院周四拒绝了Hikvision的竞标，要求取消联邦通信委员会对中国制造商生产的新视频监视和电信设备的批准。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 19:13:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/us-court-rejects-hikvision-bid-lift-fcc-ban-equipment-approvals-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>美国谴责泰国的40个Uyghurs返回中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-condemns-thailands-return-40-uyghurs-china-2025-02-27/</link><description>美国国务卿马可·卢比奥（Marco Rubio）周四谴责泰国至少40名乌耶（Uyghurs）返回中国，华盛顿说，穆斯林集团的成员面临种族灭绝。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 19:05:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-condemns-thailands-return-40-uyghurs-china-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国销售调查的前商务官员说</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/big-fines-coming-companies-with-export-violations-says-ex-commerce-official-2025-02-27/</link><description>上个月最高部门官员说，在未来几个月内，美国商务部可能会在未来几个月内向像中国这样的国家提供非法运送技术的公司处以高额罚款。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 17:07:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/big-fines-coming-companies-with-export-violations-says-ex-commerce-official-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>美国商务提名人说</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/report-tsmc-chips-made-huawei-huge-concern-us-commerce-nominee-says-2025-02-27/</link><description>美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的提名人周四负责监督出口政策，称台湾半导体制造业公司共同生产了成千上万的筹码，这些筹码进入了中国的华为，这是“巨大的关注”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 16:53:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/report-tsmc-chips-made-huawei-huge-concern-us-commerce-nominee-says-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>苹果提起手表的“碳中性”主张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-sued-over-carbon-neutral-claim-watches-2025-02-27/</link><description>苹果曾被消费者起诉，他们说其说明三种版本的苹果手表是“碳中性”的，环保友好的是虚假和误导性的。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 15:30:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-sued-over-carbon-neutral-claim-watches-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>COP30总裁说</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/china-plays-key-role-climate-change-may-be-looked-additional-leadership-cop30-2025-02-27/</link><description>COP30主席安德烈·阿兰哈·科雷亚·洛戈（Andre Aranha Correa do Lago Lago）周四表示，中国在应对气候变化方面起着非常重要的作用，其他人可能会寻求亚洲国家的额外领导地位。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 15:23:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/china-plays-key-role-climate-change-may-be-looked-additional-leadership-cop30-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>巴西食品加工机说2025年食品销售超出了期望</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/brazil-food-processor-says-2025-food-sales-exceed-expectations-2025-02-27/</link><description>高管周四表示，上市的肉类加工商BRF周四表示，食品销售超出了巴西的头两个月的预期，该公司计划扩大加工食品的生产，以从强劲的需求中获取收入。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 15:22:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/brazil-food-processor-says-2025-food-sales-exceed-expectations-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>洛根集团（Logan Group）从80％</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/logan-group-secures-backing-over-80-creditors-8-billion-debt-revamp-2025-02-27/</link><description>总部位于深圳的房地产开发商洛根集团（Logan Group）周四表示，已获得80.8％以上债权人的重组提案的支持，他们共同持有62.1亿美元的未偿还离岸债务。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 15:04:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/logan-group-secures-backing-over-80-creditors-8-billion-debt-revamp-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普誓言3月4日对加拿大墨西哥的关税，中国超过芬太尼的10％</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/trump-says-mexico-canada-tariffs-take-effect-march-4-2025-02-27/</link><description>美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）周四表示，他提议对墨西哥的25％关税，加拿大商品将于3月4日生效，同时对中国进口商品的额外关税，因为致命毒品仍在从这些国家涌入美国。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 13:56:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/trump-says-mexico-canada-tariffs-take-effect-march-4-2025-02-27/</guid></item></channel></rss>